# UI Component Guidelines
## Collapsible Sections
- Use the isOpen state pattern for collapsible sections
- Include a visual indicator for collapsed/expanded state
- Maintain consistent animation timing (200ms)

## Modals
- Place modals at the root level of the component
- Use Flowbite's Modal component for consistency
- Include proper aria labels and roles
- Handle escape key and click outside for closing

## Lists and Items
- Use consistent spacing between items (space-y-4)
- Maintain consistent padding and margins
- Use grid or flex layouts for item content
- Include proper hover and focus states
